05:30.746 --> 05:31.872
Stop it!

05:42.158 --> 05:43.489
Look! Look!

05:49.232 --> 05:50.529
Oh! Whoa!

06:00.009 --> 06:02.204
Hey, hey!
Look, look! Trekkers!

06:02.311 --> 06:03.539
