but you'll sure want more.

07:36.539 --> 07:38.006
As long as all your
permits are updated

07:38.107 --> 07:39.597
and so on.
Yeah, yeah. See?

07:41.376 --> 07:43.970
Okay. Yeah. 'Cause the rangers
do get out and work the trail.

07:44.078 --> 07:45.102
So, you want to keep
these close, Cliff.

07:45.213 --> 07:46.180
All right.

07:46.314 --> 07:47.747
