07:50.551 --> 07:51.518
Did you miss me?

07:51.619 --> 07:53.086
You know, three days
sounds plenty to me.

07:58.860 --> 08:01.090
Nine whole minutes.

08:01.529 --> 08:02.655
Do you realize

08:02.764 --> 08:05.528
that's the longest we've been
apart since we got married?

08:05.633 --> 08:07.601
You must have missed
me something awful.

08:07.702 --> 08:10.398
