1,000 feet of elevation.

08:30.124 --> 08:31.216
That's the killer.

08:31.325 --> 08:32.815
I missed you, too, baby.

08:32.927 --> 08:35.327
What?
Did you go somewhere?

08:35.429 --> 08:37.193
You're so bad!

08:37.298 --> 08:39.265
$475.35.

08:39.366 --> 08:40.390
All right.

08:41.135 --> 08:43.000
Yeah, I know. It looks
like I robbed a bank.

08:43.104 --> 08:45.572
It's our wedding haul!

08:45.673 --> 08:46.935
What's up? What's up?

08:48.242 --> 08:50.039
- How's my baby boy?
- Back from Oahu?

08:50.244 --> 08:51.211
Glad to see you back.

08:51.312 --> 08:52.472
Nowhere near
Honolulu, were you?

08:52.580 --> 08:55.071
No, on the other side. Waves
were junk for three days.

08:55.183 --> 08:58.584
More better over here. Why?
What's the stink in 'Lulu?

08:59.120 --> 09:03.352
