with your bags.

09:12.233 --> 09:13.564
Get an early
start, brother.

09:13.668 --> 09:14.794
Yeah, I will.

09:46.501 --> 09:48.230
<i>...never falter</i>

09:48.803 --> 09:53.069
<i>I need your love
each and every day</i>

09:56.777 --> 09:58.039
<i>All right</i>

10:02.650 --> 10:03.912
