10:28.876 --> 10:32.107
Come on. Nothing bad ever
happens in Hawaii, right?

10:39.618 --> 10:40.607
So, how far are you going?

10:40.720 --> 10:41.948
Lumahai Beach.

10:42.054 --> 10:45.455
Lumahai? Lumahai? I don't
think we know that area.

10:45.558 --> 10:48.425
It's about 10 miles ahead,
right on this road,

10:48.527 --> 10:49.789
right by where
the big trail is.

10:50.062 --> 10:51.120
You know that trail?

10:51.230 --> 10:52.993
Yeah, the big trail?

10:56.669 --> 11:00.662
But we're... But we're
not going that far. So...

11:04.043 --> 11:05.943
So, how far do you go?

11:06.078 --> 11:10.014
Uh... Just up
the road a bit.

11:10.916 --> 11:13.908
So, if you guys, you know,
stay here for five more minutes,

11:14.019 --> 11:15.111
I'm sure someone will
come along that can...

11:15.221 --> 11:18.088
We was waiting for, like,
an hour before you stopped.

11:18.190 --> 11:19.521
Maybe more.

11:19.959 --> 11:22.587
Shit, I thought
this was Hawaii.

11:22.695 --> 11:23.753
Sorry.

11:24.730 --> 11:26.095
Come on.

11:27.733 --> 11:29.758
Hey, you guys married?

11:29.869 --> 11:31.666
Yeah, yeah,
we just got married.

11:32.104 --> 11:35.403
Hold this. Some of these
pictures totally suck.

11:35.508 --> 11:37.237
It's one of those
cameras you chuck.

11:37.343 --> 11:39.368
- This one, this is a good one.
- Hey, Cleo, what are you doing?

11:39.478 --> 11:41.139
These people want to
see less of us, not more.

11:41.247 --> 11:42.578
Here it is.

11:44.583 --> 11:46.312
That's us doing
the deed in Oahu.

11:46.585 --> 11:47.574
Wow.

11:47.686 --> 11:50.382
We just woke up one morning
and decided to get married.

11:50.556 --> 11:51.682
Pretty, isn't it?

11:51.791 --> 11:53.725
Yeah, it's lovely.
It's...

11:54.827 --> 11:57.295
Wait. Is this in
a grocery store?

11:57.396 --> 12:00.126
Paula's Market. They do
it up real nice for you.

12:00.232 --> 12:02.132
Yeah, yeah, yeah.
There's an onion.

12:02.234 --> 12:04.964
Yeah, produce manager
took that picture.

12:05.571 --> 12:06.902
I know it sounds
kind of tacky,

12:07.006 --> 12:08.667
