We could have been there by now.

12:32.431 --> 12:34.194
Maybe next time, huh?

12:35.467 --> 12:37.560
Kale, don't be that way.

12:37.703 --> 12:38.761
Baby, come on.

12:38.871 --> 12:39.860
Come on, guys.

12:40.606 --> 12:41.800
We don't have to make
this a bigger deal...

12:41.907 --> 12:44.933
Cleo, get the fuck
out of this man's ride!

13:05.831 --> 13:09.130
Well, I think we
handled that really well.

13:16.075 --> 13:17.269
<i>Up there!</i>

13:17.376 --> 13:19.071
<i>Here we go.
Kalalau Trail.</i>

13:19.879 --> 13:21.813
- That's good.
- Bye, Mom!

13:22.748 --> 13:24.648
Well, I was just
pointing and shooting.

13:24.750 --> 13:26.513
These new things have
too many buttons for me.

13:26.619 --> 13:29.110
