14:38.457 --> 14:40.220
Oh, my God!
Careful.

14:42.227 --> 14:43.251
You got it.

14:43.362 --> 14:44.488
Okay. Thank you.

14:45.497 --> 14:47.897
You did great.

14:48.000 --> 14:49.365
Come on, baby,
you can do it.

15:06.819 --> 15:08.184
Outstanding.

15:09.088 --> 15:10.749
Did I almost just
die right there?

15:10.856 --> 15:12.483
Come here, come here, come here.

15:12.591 --> 15:14.081
Are you okay?

15:14.193 --> 15:15.217
Yeah.

15:15.327 --> 15:16.919
I was doing so well,
