want him to do their projects.

15:51.729 --> 15:55.324
I knew I smelled fame and fortune
on you. A screenplay writer?

15:55.433 --> 15:56.866
We just say screen...
Screenwriter.

15:56.967 --> 15:59.299
Any movies I might know?

15:59.403 --> 16:01.928
Well, actually my...
