Still trying to figure that
out. Still casting out, so...

16:13.584 --> 16:15.814
Well, Nic Cage is
always money in my book.

16:15.920 --> 16:17.285
I like how he
gets all intense

16:17.388 --> 16:19.219
right at
the end of a sentence!

16:19.323 --> 16:21.052
So, you got
a good Act 2 twist?

16:21.158 --> 16:22.147
Yeah.

16:22.259 --> 16:23.726
Yeah?
It's...

16:25.162 --> 16:27.027
Are you in
the business, Nick?

16:27.131 --> 16:29.998
Me? No, no.
I just took some course,

16:30.101 --> 16:32.331
one of those
writing boot camps.

16:32.436 --> 16:34.631
I've had so many ass-puckering
