17:44.441 --> 17:48.775
No. That's fucked up. That's your
vision, Cliff. That's your baby.

17:48.879 --> 17:50.676
You can't let them
get away with that shit.

17:50.781 --> 17:53.079
He's got these agents
and they don't do...

17:53.184 --> 17:55.243
I mean, they don't
fight for him or anything.

17:55.352 --> 17:56.683
And I was just telling
Cliff the other day...

17:56.787 --> 17:59.017
Not that "me" isn't
my favorite subject,

17:59.123 --> 18:01.648
but maybe we could talk about
something else for a while.

18:01.759 --> 18:04.751
Well, I'm going to leave you
with one last pearl of wisdom.

18:06.563 --> 18:09.031
Get a new agent?
You get a new story.

18:13.036 --> 18:14.765
What?
Me, too!

18:14.871 --> 18:16.839
I have one! No!
