they only just met.

50:58.190 --> 50:59.623
Yeah.

51:02.494 --> 51:03.552
Yeah.

51:34.693 --> 51:35.682
Hey, what you doing?

51:38.463 --> 51:40.829
Cliff, yeah?
Cliff Anderson.

51:42.834 --> 51:43.926
What are you doing?

51:44.035 --> 51:45.627
I thought that was you, but then
